Date: Sat, 27 May 2017 17:44:19 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915/gvt: Return -EIO if host GuC submission is enabled when loading GVT-g
Git-commit: ecef814c994d7d00dfa7bef5aa87dd66e8574946
Patch-mainline: v4.13-rc1
References: FATE#322643 bsc#1055900

Currently GVT-g cannot work properly when host GuC submission is
enabled, so make the driver loading failed in this case.

V2: 
- use DRM_ERROR as it is a fatal message. (Chris)

